  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, I am your English chat partner. It's a pleasure to meet you — I'm excited to practice English with you. How was your day so far?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi Maya, nice to meet you too! My day was okay, just studying for NEET PG. Lot of books, some stress. How about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You're doing great — studying that much is no joke. How do you usually relax after a heavy study session?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hmm, I try to cook sometimes. Makes me feel better. Or I listen to some classical music. What do you do to relax?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Cooking or classical music — both sound calming. I get that. What kind of music do you like?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Mainly Hindustani classical, but I enjoy Carnatic too. It's like... \"shanti\" comes to my mind while listening. How about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said \"shanti\" — I get that. Peace feels rare these days. What brings peace to you most?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Most times, cooking for family brings peace. Also, when I read a good book. But lately, exams stress me out, \"aapka kya hain\"?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You said 'aapka kya hain' — I get that. Exams stress everyone. What helps you most when stress builds up."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I take short walks or talk to a friend. Sometimes, just a cup of tea helps. But studies are piling up, so it's hard to find time. Gotta go now — thanks for chatting, Maya!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You're doing great — taking time for tea or walks is smart. What's one small thing you can steal back for yourself today?"
    }
  ],
